Bruce EYTINGE, Libelant-Appellant, v. William H. BERRI, Respondent-Appellee. No. 415. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. May 17, 1937. C. Walter Randall, of New York City (Crawford & Sprague, of New York City, George C. Sprague, Roy W. Chamberlain, and Nicholas Healy, III, all of New York City, of counsel), for appellant. Elliott, Jones & Fanning, of Brooklyn. (Thomas A. Shaw, of Brooklyn, of counsel), for appellee.

*1007Before MANTON, SWAN, and CHASE, Circuit Judges

PER CURIAM.

Decree affirmed..
